   "body" : "Through 0.14 branch, the estimatesmartfee API was tagged \"WARNING: This interface is unstable and may disappear or change!\" and this warning is removed for 0.15, so we should think carefully if this is the right API.   \r\n\r\nThe changes here are to make the additional parameter for conservative estimates a more general estimate_mode string , to omit the feerate and include an error string instead of returning -1 on error, and to do better parameter checking initially.\r\n\r\nIt is only the last commit, but it's built on #10706 and #10543.\r\n\r\n",
